1) py -m venv myworld
code to create an enviroment

2) py -m pip install Django
we need to install tools in our enviroment

3) django-admin startproject myProjectName
cose to create the app

4) source petShop/Scripts/activate
code to activate the enviroment from root folder

5) py manage.py startapp members
code to create an app

6) py manage.py runserver
code to start the app 

7) py manage.py migrate
when creating a new folder for entities we have to adde it to 
settings in INSTALLED_APPS then run that code

8) py manage.py makemigrations
use this code when having changes in modules before code 7)
